    <abstract>
      <t>This document specifies tunneling configuration over MAPOS (Multiple Access Protocol over SONET/SDH) networks.  Using this mode, a MAPOS network can provide transparent point-to-point link for PPP over SONET/SDH (Packet over SONET/SDH, POS) without any additional overhead.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.</t>
